graphql.query:
query GetRangeofBlocks  {
  blockRange(sBlock: 24742881, lBlock: 24742888) {
    blockHash
    blockNumber
    timestamp
    transfers {
      extrinsicHash
      module
      function
      isFinalized
      blockNumber
      fromAddress
      toAddress
      amount
      fee
      tip
      events {
        module
        function
        extrinsicHash
        extrinsicIdx
        blockNumber
        isTransferEvent
        attributes
      }
    }
    nonTransferExtrinsics {
      extrinsicHash
      module
      function
      isFinalized
      blockNumber
      events {
        module
        function
        extrinsicHash
        extrinsicIdx
        blockNumber
        isTransferEvent
        attributes
      }
    }
  }
}
